		<h4>Ingredients</h4>
		<ul class="ingredients">
			<li>1-1/4 cup of light olive oil, divided</li>
			<li>1 egg</li>
			<li>1/2 teaspoon mustard powder</li>
			<li>1/2 teaspoon salt</li>
			<li>1/2 to 1 lemon, juiced</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-6">
		<h4>Instructions</h4>
		<ol class="instructions">
			<li>Place the egg, 1/4 cup of olive oil, mustard powder, and salt in a mixing bowl, blender, or food processor. Mix thoroughly.</li>
			<li>While the food processor or blender is running (or while mixing in a bowl with a stick blender),  slowly drizzle in the remaining cup of olive oil.</li>
